 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 20px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;液压湿喷机&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;性能特点&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;1、泵送系统能耗少，工作效率高，易损件少，系统可靠性高，输送量稳定。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;2、喷射系统采用单喷头或双喷头喷浆作业， 提高了工作效率。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal; line-height: 2em;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;3、配有自动润滑系统，对主要密封部位釆用 自动润滑，油脂加注量、加注时间自动控制，大大 延长易损件寿命。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0p