; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: middle; border: none; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; line-height: 2em; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 20px;&quot;&gt;液压湿喷机生产厂家及选型指导&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;选择合适的液压湿喷机厂家非常重要，购买到性价比高的产品自然是好事；先拥有良好的售后服务好的维修人员、过硬质量的产品这样的厂家才是合适的选择；&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;我们是专业液压湿喷机生产厂家，拥有18年喷锚支护设备生产经验，主营湿喷台车系列、自动上料喷浆机组系列、液压湿喷机系列，干式混凝土喷射机系列、凿岩机、钻头钻杆系列、注浆机系列、钢筋机械系列及煤矿用产品等。公司凭借优良的品质，合理的价格，良好的服务，赢得国内外客户的一致好评，客户遍布全球100多个国家和地区！&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.ygsdjq.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202208/1661939411ae99ea.jpg&quot; title=&quot;湿喷台车装车发货&quot; alt=&quot;湿喷台车装车发货&quot; width=&quot;792&quot; height=&quot;444&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: middle; border: none; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://www.ygsdjq.com/uploadfile/ueditor/image/202208/16619188415bf82e.jpg&quot; title=&quot;喷浆设备生产车间&quot; alt=&quot;喷浆设备生产车间&quot; width=&quot;792&quot; height=&quot;792&quot; border=&quot;0&quot; vspace=&quot;0&quot; style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: middle; border: none; image-rendering: -webkit-optimize-contrast;&quot;/&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;豫工机械液压湿喷机的价格一台就是出厂价，没有任何中间商，买到的设备直接从厂家车间发货送到客户手中；让客户直接享受到更优惠价格。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#555555;font-family:Source Han Sans CN, Source Han Sans CN-Regular&quot;&gt;液压湿喷机选哪款更合适？豫工机械为您指导，我们会根据使用的流量为您；如果你对设备的生产要求是3-8m³/h，我们为您推荐90型单喷头液压湿喷机；如果你对设备的生产要求是3-6m³/h，我们为您推荐90A型单喷头液压湿喷机；如果你对设备的生产要求是12-16m³/h，我们为您推荐C-90型双喷头液压湿喷机；更多了解咨询我们为您详细解答。&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; background: transparent; font-size: 18px; outline: 0px; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; font-weight: 700; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;138-3710-3643&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(204, 0, 0); font-family: &amp;quot;Helvetica Neue&amp;quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;或者&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://pwt.zoosnet.net/LR/Chatpre.aspx?id=PWT55787204&amp;lng=cn&amp;r=&amp;rf1=http%3A//www.yglmjq.com/list-xwzx&amp;rf2=.html&amp;p=http%3A//www.yglmjq.com/show-97.html&amp;cid=8dd31af3040e4736bdbf1a296a09506b&amp;sid=8dd31af3040e4736bdbf1a296a09506b&quot; target=&quot;_self&quot; style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, &amp;quot;Microsoft YaHei&amp;quot;; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; font-weight: 700; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration-line: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: transparent; -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; border: 0px; vertical-align: baseline;&quot;&gt;在线咨询&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color:#333333;font-family:Helvetica Neue, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif&quot;&gt;。{立即咨询}&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;box-sizing: border-box; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: transparent; line-height: 2em; color: rgb(85, 85, 85); font-family: &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN&amp;quot;, &amp;quot;Source Han Sans CN-Regular&amp;quot;; white-space: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;河南豫工机械是隧道喷浆支护设备生产厂家，以“高效稳定”享誉市场，主营液压湿喷机、吊装式喷浆车、等离子切割机、钢筋网片排焊机、小导管缩尖机、小导管冲孔机、钢筋笼绕筋机、隧道风机等隧道设备，在高铁、地铁、隧道领域发挥着举足轻重的作用，被国家大批重点建设项目广泛采用，累计服务工程项目30000+